data.text:
The Cattanooga Cats is a 2025 American computer-animated fantasy adventure film written and directed by Leonardo Navarrete produced by Steven Spielberg .

Cast[]

Voice Cast[]

Nick Jonas as Country

Joe Jonas as Scoots

Kevin Jonas as Groove

Miley Cyrus as Kitty Jo

Callum Shoniker as Lambsy

Bill Fagerbakke as Bristle Hound

Production[]

Filming[]

Principal Photography Begin November 24, 2024 In Nicaragua

Filming Also Took Place In Costa Rica

Principal Photography Wrapped February 12, 2024 In Panama
